title: Guardians of Middle-Earth: Ithilien Rangers Ambush - Total War: Rise of Mordor Mod Gameplay
description:
A great force of Uruk-Hai from Isengard march deep in protected lands.  Ithilien Rangers spotted the intruders, and gather a mighty force from Gondor to meet them.  The have setup an ambush deep in the forest,  The archers are ready to kill their prey.  Enjoy the battle :D

Total War: Rise of Mordor is a mod for Total War: Attila.  The mod is still in closed alpha, but you can learn more about it here: http://www.moddb.com/mods/total-war-rise-of-mordor

Jackies Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AdBtbuHbcEg 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
